# OpenZync Frontend — Final Revamp Plan

## Decisions Consolidated

| Decision | Your Answer |
|---|---|
| Framework | **shadcn/ui + Tailwind CSS v4** (replace MUI entirely) |
| Design aesthetic | **Linear-style** minimal, clean, dark-first |
| Feature scope | **All 46 API endpoints** — build pages for every domain |
| Graph library | **D3.js** (replace react-force-graph-2d) |
| Charts | **tremor** (shadcn-native, Recharts-based) |
| Classifications/Extractions | **Sub-pages** from session detail, not tabs |

---

## Updated Technology Stack

### Add
- **shadcn/ui** (components via CLI: `button`, `card`, `dialog`, `dropdown-menu`, `table`, `tabs`, `sheet`, `badge`, `input`, `select`, `skeleton`, `breadcrumb`, `tooltip`, `command`, `toast`, `alert-dialog`, `progress`, `checkbox`, `separator`, `avatar`)
- **Tailwind CSS v4** + `tailwindcss-animate`
- **tremor** (`@tremor/react`) — chart components (AreaChart, BarChart, DonutChart)
- **D3.js** (`d3-force`, `d3-selection`) — graph visualization
- **Lucide React** — icon system
- **Inter** + **JetBrains Mono** fonts (`next/font`)
- **sonner** — toast notifications (shadcn-native)
- **next-themes** — dark/light mode management
- **cmdk** — command palette (shadcn Command uses this)

### Remove
- `@mui/material`, `@mui/icons-material`, `@mui/x-data-grid`, `@emotion/react`, `@emotion/styled`
- `recharts` (replaced by tremor)
- `react-force-graph-2d` (replaced by D3.js)
- `@fontsource/roboto`
- All custom `src/components/shared/*` — replaced by shadcn

