## Route Structure

```
/                              → redirect to /overview
/login                         → LoginPage
/signup                        → SignupPage

/overview                      → OverviewPage
/analytics                     → AnalyticsPage
/monitoring                    → MonitoringPage
/monitoring/query              → PromQueryPage

/users                         → UsersPage
/sessions                      → SessionsPage
/sessions/[id]                 → SessionDetailLayout
/sessions/[id]/messages        → MessagesTab
/sessions/[id]/facts           → FactsTab
/sessions/[id]/graph           → GraphTab
/sessions/[id]/classifications → ClassificationsPage
/sessions/[id]/extractions     → StructuredExtractionsPage

/memory                        → MemoryPage (ingest + context + search)

/graph                         → GraphExplorerPage
/graph/communities             → CommunitiesPage
/graph/facts                   → FactsPage

/audit                         → AuditLogPage

/settings                      → SettingsPage
/settings/api-keys             → ApiKeysPage
/settings/schemas              → SchemasPage
/settings/classifications      → ClassificationSchemasPage
/settings/extractions          → ExtractionSchemasPage
```

